      <title>印度尽管存在担忧，但仍通过了反洗钱审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/india-passes-anti-money-laundering-review-despite-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家全球反洗钱监管机构表示，印度基本上遵守了其规则，尽管该国需要加大对一些非金融领域预防措施的监督。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/india-passes-anti-money-laundering-review-despite-concerns</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 09:04:06 GMT</pubDate>
